Package producereportscontrollers

Class ProduceStockController

java.lang.Object
producereportscontrollers.ProduceStockController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ProduceStockController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
This class is a Produce Stock Report Controller for ProduceStockPage.fxml the function of this class is to display information generated by the system of that information are two tables that show information about the stock, the amount of sales done for each category stock percentage daily throughout the month, after reviewing the system-generated reports, the area manager is required to insert information to produce their own report for it to be submitted to the management to see This class also uses other classes to help manage the properties one of the classes is TableRow - which helps us add rows to our table of information with products sold in orders
Author:
amran, mohmad
